Package: smcryptoR
Type: Package
Title: ShangMi(SM) Cryptographic Algorithms(SM2/SM3/SM4)
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: person("Meng", "Yu", role = c("aut", "cre"), email =
        "610074@gmail.com", comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0005-9794-5522"))
Description: Bindings to 'smcrypto'
        <https://github.com/zhuobie/smcrypto>: a 'Rust' implementation
        of China's Standards of Encryption Algorithms, which is usually
        called 'ShangMi(SM)' algorithms. It contains 'SM3' message
        digest algorithm, 'SM2' asymmetric encryption algorithm and
        'SM4' symmetric encryption algorithm. Users can do message
        hash, encrypt/decrypt, sign/verify, key exchange and more.
